sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Staff
    participant Kong as Kong Gateway
    participant Verify as Verification Orchestrator
    participant Redis as Redis Lock
    participant Ticket as Ticket Service
    participant Event as Event Service
    participant SeatInv as Seat Inventory Service
    participant Log as Ticket Log Service

    Staff->>Kong: POST /verify/scan
    Kong->>Verify: qrHash
    Verify->>Ticket: lookup ticket by QR hash
    Ticket-->>Verify: ticket record
    Verify->>Redis: acquire scan_lock:{ticketId}
    Redis-->>Verify: lock granted
    Verify->>Event: load event
    Event-->>Verify: event details
    Verify->>SeatInv: check inventory for sold seat
    SeatInv-->>Verify: seat is sold
    Verify->>Log: fetch prior scan logs
    Log-->>Verify: not yet checked in
    Verify->>Ticket: PATCH status=used
    Verify->>Log: POST checked_in audit log
    Verify->>Redis: release scan lock
    Verify-->>Staff: 200 valid ticket
